# 止蝕

(pos:動詞)
<explanation>
yue:投資或交易嗰陣，為咗防止繼續虧損，而將手上嘅股票、基金或者其他投資產品賣走或者平倉。簡單啲講，就係「停手唔再蝕」噉解。
eng:to stop loss; to cut losses (in finance/investment)
<eg>
yue:隻股票跌咗三成，我即刻止蝕，唔想再落去。
eng:The stock dropped by 30%, so I immediately stopped the loss; I didn't want to lose any more.

<eg>
yue:投資要識得止蝕，唔好死坐。
eng:You need to know when to cut losses in investment; don't just hold on stubbornly.
 [end of text]


